Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2024-hardeep-singh-puri-no-discrimination-flimsy-hardeep-puri-slams-opposition-in-budget-row-6179411%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Man%20Cheats%20US%20Woman%20Of%20%24400%2C000.%20Probe%20Agency%20Explains%20How%20He%20Did%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELisa%20Roth%2C%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20US%2C%20got%20a%20call%20on%20July%204%2C%202023%2C%20from%20a%20person%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bagent%20of%20Microsoft%26quot%3B.%20He%20asked%20her%20to%20transfer%20%24400%2C000%20dollars%20to%20a%20cryptocurrency%20wallet.%20Little%20did%20Ms%20Roth%20know%20that%20she%20had%20fallen%20victim%20to%20a%20cyber%20fraud%20and%20was%20duped%20of%20Rs%203.3%20crore%20(%24400%2C000).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20arrested%20a%20bookie%20and%20a%20cryptocurrency%20handler%20based%20out%20of%20Delhi.%20Lakshya%20Vij%2C%20the%20bookie%2C%20lives%20in%20east%20Delhi's%20Dilshad%20Garden%20and%20his%20name%20surfaced%20when%20last%20year%20in%20March%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20arrested%20him%20from%20the%20Cross%20River%20Mall%20in%20east%20Delhi%20and%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20got%20him%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Woman%20Was%20Duped%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20transferred%20by%20Ms%20Roth%20went%20to%20the%20wallets%20of%20Praful%20Gupta%20and%20his%20mother%20Sarita%20Gupta.%20During%20the%20investigation%2C%20it%20was%20also%20found%20that%20a%20person%20named%20Karan%20Chug%20was%20getting%20this%20money%20from%20Gupta%20and%20deposited%20it%20in%20different%20wallets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20this%20amount%20was%20transferred%20to%20different%20Indian%20bogus%20accounts%20by%20selling%20a%20cryptocurrency%20and%20the%20money%20was%20transferred%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Karan%20and%20Lakshya.%20Later%2C%20they%20used%20the%20money%20received%20from%20people%20on%20betting%20apps%20like%20Fair%20Play%2024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20raided%20several%20places%20last%20month%20and%20recovered%20digital%20evidence.%20Statements%20of%20those%20who%20owned%20the%20crypto%20wallets%20that%20were%20used%20in%20the%20crime%20were%20also%20recorded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20investigation%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20money%20was%20transferred%20to%20all%20the%20wallets%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Lakshya%20and%20he%20is%20the%20mastermind%20of%20this%20fraud.%20The%20main%20accused%20was%20produced%20in%20Delhi's%20Rouse%20Avenue%20Court%20from%20where%20he%20has%20been%20sent%20on%205-day%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721830080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fb2bakn3_delhi-crypto-fraud-accused_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-man-cheats-us-woman-of-400-000-probe-agency-explains-how-he-did-it-6179385%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lisa%20Roth%2C%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20US%2C%20got%20a%20call%20on%20July%204%2C%202023%2C%20from%20a%20person%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bagent%20of%20Microsoft%26quot%3B.%20He%20asked%20her%20to%20transfer%20%24400%2C000%20dollars%20to%20a%20cryptocurrency%20wallet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-man-cheats-us-woman-of-400-000-probe-agency-explains-how-he-did-it-6179385%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-man-cheats-us-woman-of-400-000-probe-agency-explains-how-he-did-it-6179385%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-man-cheats-us-woman-of-400-000-probe-agency-explains-how-he-did-it-6179385%2Fa