2C%20guests%20can%20pick%20at%20the%20mound%20of%20poached%20seafood%20and%20freshly%20carved%20meats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20the%20buffet%20transforms%20into%20the%20ship's%20go-to%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%20Italian%20restaurant%20in%20the%20evening.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bread%20and%20small%20appetizers%20on%20%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668302811aace5b3ada33bda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurants%20all%20come%20with%20complimentary%20bread.%20Pictured%20is%20the%20bread%20selection%20from%20La%20Terraza.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELa%20Terraza's%20dinner%20menu%20has%20two%20sections%3A%20one%20%26quot%3Bclassic%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20%26quot%3Badventure.%26quot%3B%20(Have%20you%20noticed%20the%20dual%20menu%20trend%20yet%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPurists%20could%20opt%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20stuffed%20calamari%20and%20pasta%20alla%20norma%20(pasta%20with%20eggplants).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20those%20keen%20on%20the%20adventure%20menu%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Tonet%2C%20was%20designed%20to%20showcase%20contemporary%20Italian%20food%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurant%20also%20has%20selections%20like%20whipped%20mortadella%20with%20pecorino%20chips%20and%20grilled%20seabass%20with%20stuffed%20cabbage%20and%20an%20anchovy-Processo%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you'd%20prefer%20a%20dinner%20and%20a%20show%2C%20head%20to%20Silver%20Note.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plate%20of%20food%20at%20Silver%20Note%20on%20%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668568e21aace5b3ada41a72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESilver%20Note%20has%2054%20seats%20and%20a%20bar%20for%20post-dinner%20drinks%20with%20live%20music.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%2C%20travelers%20are%20serenaded%20by%20a%20jazz%20pianist%20and%20singer%20while%20they%20dine%20on%20small%2C%20refined%20plates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFood%20options%20are%20as%20casual%20as%20vegetable%20dumplings%20served%20in%20a%20hot%20stone-like%20dish%20and%20as%20whimsical%20as%20a%20triple-chocolate%20dessert%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20swan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20music%20options%2C%20that%20depends%20on%20the%20performers.%20But%20expect%20to%20hear%20classics%20from%20recognizable%20figures%20like%20Frank%20Sinatra%20and%20Bill%20Withers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Arts%20Cafe%20isn't%20technically%20a%20restaurant%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20great%20place%20to%20grab%20a%20quick%20and%20light%20bite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20of%20arts%20cafe%20and%20tea%20on%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66856a311aace5b3ada41ca7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoffee%20and%20tea%20are%20complimentary%20on%20Silversea.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEspresso%20and%20tea%20take%20center%20stage%20at%20the%20daytime%20caf%C3%A9.%20But%20if%20you're%20feeling%20peckish%20before%20dinner%20or%20craving%20a%20do-it-yourself%20afternoon%20tea%2C%20Arts%20Cafe%20is%20where%20you'll%20want%20to%20go%20for%20cucumber%20sandwiches%20and%20slices%20of%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20same%20goes%20for%20room%20service%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20count%20caviar%20as%20a%20'light%20bite.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plates%20of%20food%20next%20to%20balcony%20overlooking%20ocean%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a00b102d66759f66fd850b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoom%20service%20is%20complimentary%20on%20Silver%20Ray.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20the%20late-night%20munchies%20coming%20on%3F%20Call%20room%20service%20to%20order%20cruise%20ship%20classics%20like%20hamburgers%20and%20hot%20dogs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOr%2C%20if%20you're%20feeling%20particularly%20fancy%2C%20you%20could%20have%20foie%20gras%20or%20caviar%20delivered%20to%20your%20door.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYes%2C%20room%20service%20caviar%20is%20complimentary%20and%20served%20with%20classic%20accouterments%20like%20sour%20cream%20and%20bellinis.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22caviar%20on%20a%20table%20in%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66830212268f62ba18a65028%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crew%20member%20who%20delivered%20my%20caviar%20and%20set%20up%20my%20dining%20table%20told%20me%20that%20caviar%20was%20among%20the%20most%20popular%20room%20service%20orders.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20the%20best%20caviar%20I've%20ever%20had%20(it's%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcalvisiususa.com%2Fcollections%2Fcaviar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalvisius'%20cheapest%20options%3C%2Fa%3E).%20But%20if%20you%20woke%20from%20your%20mid-afternoon%20nap%20craving%20a%20small%20snack%2C%20the%20salty%20little%20fish%20eggs%20certainly%20hit%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20over-the-top%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20just%20a%20tad%20bit%20pretentious%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi