ing%20the%20chief%20minister's%20speech%2C%20an%20increasingly%20angry%20Mr%20Kumar%20launched%20into%20a%20tirade%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EArre%20mahila%20ho%2C%20kuch%20jaanti%20nahin%20ho%3F%20Arre%20bol%20rahi%20hai%2C%20kahan%20se%20aate%3F%20Yeh%20logo%20ne%20kabhi%20mahila%20ko%20aage%20badhaya%20tha%3F%20Bol%20rahi%20ho%3F%20Faltu.%20Isliye%20ham%20keh%20rahe%20hai%2C%20chup%20chaap%20suno.%20Arre%20kya%20hua%3F%20Sunoge%20nahin%3F%20Hum%20to%20sunayenge.%20Agar%20aap%20nahin%20suniyega%2C%20to%20aap%20logo%20ki%20galti%20hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(You%20are%20a%20woman%2C%20don't%20you%20know%20anything%3F%20Look%2C%20she%20is%20talking.%20Have%20you%20%5Bthe%20opposition%5D%20done%20anything%20for%20women%3F%20We%20will%20talk%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20listen%2C%20its%20your%20%5Bthe%20opposition's%5D%20fault.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20opposition%20erupted%20and%20the%20slogan-shouting%20got%20louder%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20carried%20on%20with%20his%20speech%2C%20insisting%20that%20his%20government%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20the%20chief%20minister's%20remarks%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20posted%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3B'You%20are%20a%20woman%2C%20do%20you%20know%20anything%3F'%20Making%20cheap%2C%20unwanted%2C%20uncivilised%2C%20rude%20and%20low-level%20comments%20against%20women%20has%20become%20a%20habit%20of%20Honourable%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20and%20worrying%20issue%20for%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20lewd%20comment%20on%20the%20beauty%20of%20a%20BJP%20woman%20MLA%20from%20the%20tribal%20class.%20Today%2C%20he%20made%20a%20comment%20on%20two-time%20Scheduled%20Caste%20woman%20MLA%20Rekha%20Paswan.%20Honourable%20Shri%20Nitish%20ji%20has%20become%20the%20greatest%20knower%2C%20meditator%2C%20interp