%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a0d0452d66759f66fda22e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20passenger%20plane%20crashed%20on%20takeoff%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20killing%2018%20of%20the%2019%20people%20onboard.%3Cp%3EPRAKASH%20MATHEMA%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E18%20people%20have%20died%20after%20a%20small%20passenger%20plane%20crashed%20during%20takeoff%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20Nepal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENepal%20has%20a%20poor%20aviation%20safety%20record%20and%20all%20of%20its%20airlines%20are%20banned%20from%20European%20airspace.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKathmandu's%20challenging%20weather%20and%20high%20altitude%20make%20it%20a%20difficult%20place%20to%20fly%2C%20an%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E18%20people%20have%20died%20after%20a%20small%20passenger%20airplane%20crashed%20during%20takeoff%20in%20Nepal's%20capital%20city%2C%20Kathmandu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane's%20captain%20is%20the%20only%20remaining%20survivor%20of%20the%2019%20onboard%2C%20including%20two%20crew%20members%20and%2017%20technicians%20of%20the%20airline%2C%20who%20were%20traveling%20to%20Pokhara%2C%20reportedly%20for%20aircraft%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saurya%20Airlines%20flight%20skidded%20off%20the%20runway%20at%20approximately%2011.15%20a.m.%20local%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fprovince-no-3%2F2024%2F07%2F24%2Fcaan-confirms-18-aboard-saurya-airlines-dead-one-rescued%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Kathmandu%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%2018%20bodies%20have%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20crash%20site%20at%20the%20Tribhuvan%20International%20Airport%20in%20Nepal.%20The%20pilot%2C%20Captain%20Manish%20Ratna%20Shkya%2C%20was%20rescued%20and%20is%20being%20treated%20for%20injuries%20at%20Kathmandu%20Medical%20College%20and%20Teaching%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20and%20photos%20posted%20online%20showed%20billows%20of%20black%20smoke%20emerging%20from%20the%20wreckage%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20then%20on%20fire%20but%20since%20put%20out%20by%20firefighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20and%20rescue%20coordination%20of%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20Nepal%20said%20in%20a%20recently%20released%20statement%20that%20the%20plane%20%26quot%3Bveered%20off%20to%20the%20right%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20east%20side%20of%20the%20runway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRescue%20operations%20were%20initiated%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fire%20was%20brought%20under%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-nepal-has-so-many-fatal-plane-crashes-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENepal%20has%20a%20poor%20aviation%20safety%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20often%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20countries%20for%20air%20travel.%20All%20Nepali%20air%20carriers%20are%20banned%20from%20entering%20the%20airspace%20of%20any%20European%20Union%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftransport.ec.europa.eu%2Fdocument%2Fdownload%2F3195fabb-7575-4db9-85b9-ec5a77b481aa_en%3Ffilename%3Dair-safety-list-2024-05-30_en.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20EU%20Air%20Safety%20List%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20Aviation%20Safety%20Agency%20bans%20airlines%20from%20operating%20in%20the%20EU%20%3Cspan%3Efor%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20applicable%20international%20safety%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Ron%20Bartch%2C%20chairman%20and%20founding%20director%20of%20aviation%20consultancy%20firm%20AvLaw%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20one%20reason%20for%20its%20poor%20safety%20record%20is%20that%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20Nepal%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20terribly%20well-resourced%20safety%20regulator.%26quo