0strike%20a%20balance%20as%20it%20announced%20a%20liberal%20allocation%20for%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%20without%20yielding%20ground%20on%20the%20state's%20demand%20for%20a%20'special'%20status%20or%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShowing%20political%20dexterity%2C%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20announced%20that%20the%20Budget%20proposes%20to%20support%20several%20standalone%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20state.%20Under%20this%2C%20Rs%2026%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20allocated%20for%20developing%20four%20specific%20road%20projects%2C%20Rs%2021%2C400%20crore%20is%20earmarked%20for%20power%20projects%2C%20including%20a%20new%202%2C400%20MW%20plant%20at%20Pirpainti%2C%20and%20Rs%2011%2C500%20crore%20has%20been%20set%20aside%20for%20flood%20management.%20New%20airports%2C%20medical%20colleges%20and%20sports%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20state%20were%20part%20of%20the%20promises.%20Sitharaman%20also%20said%20additional%20allocation%20would%20be%20made%20to%20support%20capital%20investments%20and%20that%20the%20Centre%20would%20expedite%20the%20requests%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Government%20for%20external%20assistance%20from%20multilateral%20development%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMutual%20Dependence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20was%20swift%20to%20appreciate%20the%20package%2C%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20stating%20that%20though%20he%20had%20initially%20been%20pressing%20for%20special%20status%20for%20Bihar%2C%20the%20state%20has%20now%20got%20special%20aid.%20JD(U)%20spokesperson%20K.C.%20Tyagi%20estimated%20the%20allocations%20would%20touch%20Rs.%201%20Lakh%20crore%2C%20which%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20building%20an%20'Atmanirbhar'%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20is%20headed%20for%20assembly%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20to%20retain%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20JD(U)%20has%20held%20the%20reins%20in%20Bihar%20for%20two%20decades%20now%2C%20with%20relations%20with%20the%20BJP%20changing%20frequently.%20Nitish%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20'Sushashan%20Babu'%20in%20his%20home%20state%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20he%20will%20be%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%20by%20both%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)-led%20opposition%20front%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20latter%20would%20like%20to%20occupy%20prime%20political%20space%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20NDA%20has%20taken%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20as%20it%20humours%20a%20leader%20known%20for%20his%20political%20flip-flops.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20the%20dependence%20is%20mutual.%20While%20the%20BJP%20needs%20the%20JD(U)%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20Nitish%20needs%20to%20prove%20to%20his%20electorate%20that%20his%20prime%20objective%2C%20irrespective%20of%20his%20political%20flip-flops%2C%20is%20to%20secure%20the%20best%20deal%20for%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Bihar%20Package%20Includes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aforementioned%20allocations%20for%20Bihar%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20plans%20for%20supporting%20the%20development%20of%20an%20industrial%20node%20at%20Gaya%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Amritsar-Kolkata%20Industrial%20Corridor.%20The%20idea%20to%20develop%20the%20node%20at%20Gaya%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20was%20centred%20around%20the%20motto%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EVikas%20bhi%20Virasat%20bhi%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20is%2C%20development%20around%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20has%20also%20been%20made%20part%20of%20a%20grand%20'Purvodaya%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20which%20covers%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20aims%20to%20push%20a