olve%20led%20him%20to%20utilise%20the%20small%20patch%20outside%20his%20home%20%E2%80%93%20once%20a%20dumping%20ground%20for%20garbage%20%E2%80%93%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20my%20village%2C%20I%20used%20to%20plant%20many%20trees%20along%20with%20my%20father.%20But%20when%20my%20family%20moved%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20work%2C%20there%20was%20not%20much%20space%20in%20the%20new%20house%20to%20plant%20trees.%20I%20noticed%20how%20people%20would%20throw%20garbage%20outside%20our%20house.%20So%2C%20we%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20garden.%20Today%2C%20this%20spot%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20place%20for%20passersby%20to%20stop%20and%20take%20selfies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%2C%20Manoj%20has%20pursued%20his%20green%20endeavours%20despite%20initially%20facing%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20whenever%20I%20planted%20saplings%2C%20they%20were%20either%20plucked%20or%20taken%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Manoj%20remained%20undeterred.%20He%20persisted%20by%20using%20recycled%20objects%20including%20old%20oil%20cans%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332003%2Fmother-daughter-duo-from-kerala-upcycle-waste-to-make-planters-sustainable-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20tires%2C%20and%20helmets%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20planting%20to%20ensure%20that%20potential%20theft%20would%20not%20be%20a%20setback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20garden%20boasts%20over%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20in%20a%20compact%20space%20of%2010%20ft%20by%204%20ft.%20He%20chose%20plants%20that%20thrive%20in%20limited%20sunlight%2C%20as%20a%20large%20tree%20already%20shades%20the%20area.%20He%20opted%20for%20seasonal%20flowers%20and%20ornamental%20plants%2C%20intentionally%20avoiding%20species%20commonly%20used%20in%20religious%20practices%20to%20discourage%20plucking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarkably%2C%20this%20roadside%20garden%E2%80%99s%20beauty%20is%20a%20collective%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20including%20his%20two%20daughters%2C%20Ananya%20and%20Manisha%20Dubey%2C%20have%20actively%20helped%20flourish%20the%20garden.%20They%20decorate%20the%20space%20with%20colourful%20bricks%20and%20creatively%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356071%2Fhow-to-grow-plants-in-recycled-plastic-containers-old-bottles-urban-gardeners-share-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycled%20pots.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20initiative%20has%20inspired%20neighbours%2C%20sparking%20a%20trend%20of%20roadside%20gardens%20throughout%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%E2%80%99s%20garden%20has%20also%20become%20a%20local%20attraction%2C%20with%20people%20passing%20by%20just%20to%20enjoy%20the%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20personal%20passion%20project%20has%20become%20a%20community%20highlight.%20This%20showcases%20how%20urban%20spaces%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20lush%20gardens%20and%20proves%20that%20anyone%20can%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20their%20surroundings%2C%20regardless%20of%20space%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20lead%2C%20you%20too%20can%20transform%20vacant%20spaces%20around%20your%20house%20into%20thriving%20gardens%20and%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20your%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721800949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Manoj%20Ranjan's%20family%20moved%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20work%2C%20space%20constraints%20hindered%20his%20gardening%20passion.%20Observing%20people%20dumping%20garbage%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20area%20int