anisations%20by%20initiating%20conversations%20and%20influencing%20decisions%20by%20showcasing%20that%20hiring%20based%20on%20DEI%20(Diversity%2C%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion)%20is%20the%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha%20Sable%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Vividhataa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open-to-all%20DEI%20seminar%2Fconference%20was%20attended%20by%20corporate%20delegates%20along%20with%20students%2C%20researchers%2C%20experts%2C%20DE%26amp%3BI%20advocates%2C%20and%20similar%20activists%20from%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20panel%20discussions%2C%20fireside%20chats%2C%20and%20interactive%20workshops%20such%20as%20one-on-one%20sign%20language%20were%20held%20at%20the%20event.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20promoting%20empathy%20and%20understanding%2C%20Vividhataa%20plans%20to%20make%20DEI%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20and%20global%20MNCs%20across%20India%20through%20its%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20in%202020%20and%20traditional%20job%20fairs%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20place%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Vividhataa%20filled%20the%20gap%20by%20launching%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%201st%20Virtual%20Diversity%20Job%20Fair%202020%E2%80%9D%20to%20support%20minority%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20fair%20saw%20lots%20of%20diverse%20candidates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%20working%20from%20places%20where%20Amazon%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20offices%2C%20they%20were%20given%20WFH%20opportunities.%20A%20laptop%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20every%20other%20work%20equipment%20that%20they%20might%20need%20were%20also%20provided%20by%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20word%20of%20the%20job%20fair%20had%20spread%20around%2C%20organisations%20which%20previously%20were%20not%20big%20on%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20had%20shown%20up%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20on%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisha%20says%20that%20to%20her%20knowledge%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20organisations%20that%20work%20for%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20but%20are%20only%20restricted%20to%20a%20few%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%20is%20the%20only%20pan-India%20organisation%20working%20for%20the%20community%2C%20and%20that%20Disha%20is%20an%20internationally-acclaimed%20para%20athlete%2C%20her%20organisation%20came%20into%20the%20limelight%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-500x271.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-768x417.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-150x81.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357969%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20represented%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20various%20marathons.%20At%20every%20chance%20I%20got%2C%20I%20advocated%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20and%20others%20have%20seen%20our%20community%20grow%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20talking%20about%20the%20job%20fair%2C%20Disha%20says%20that%20in%20an%20average%20scenario%2C%20if%20there%20are%2050%20applicants%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20among%20them%20has%20a%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%2Fshe%20may%20feel%20lost.%20But%20at%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20know%20that%20their%20education%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20what%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20is%20all%20that%20matters%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVilas%20Dahipale%2C%20an%20LPI%20member%20based%20in%20Pune%20who%20was%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20holds%20an%20engineering%20degree%20but%20got%20rejected%20by%20over%2020%20companies.%20After%20a%20relative%20helped%20him%20get%20a%20job%2C%20he%20worked%20without%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20he%20updated%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20skills%20such%20as%20automation%20testing%2C%20and%20after%20a%20span%20of%20over%203%20years%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20offered%20a%20job%20at%20Accenture%20with%20a%20pick-up%2Fdrop-off%20service%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20job%20fair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20companies%20take%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20online%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20consider%20you%20as%20a%20candidate%20if%20you%20have%20a%20disability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20After%20switching%20various%20fields%20upon%20realising%20his%20limitations%20(for%20instance%2C%20field%20work%20was%20taxing%20for%20Vilas%20given%20his%20height)%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20he%20could%20only%20do%20office-based%20or%20remote%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admits%20that%20he%20was%20initially%20unaware%20that%20companies%20offer%20jobs%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20%E2%80%9CLearning%20that%20there%20was%20a%20separate%20%E2%80%98handicapped%E2%80%99%20category%20on%20job%20portals%20was%20a%20revelation%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Vilas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20revealed%20his%20condition%20on%20job%20portals%2C%20he%20started%20receiving%20calls%20from%20employees%20who%20were%20looking%20to%20hire%20handicapped%20candidates.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20saddest%20part%20is%20that%20most%20companies%20who%20are%20open%20to%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20are%20MNCs%20from%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20not%20Indian%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20rues%20Vilas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakruthi%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20LPI%20member%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20do%20her%20postgraduate%20diploma%20in%20management.%20She%20says%20that%20she%20is%20afraid%20employers%20won%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20her%20as%20a%20real%20candidate%20due%20to%20her%20height%2C%20but%20the%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20she%20has%20the%20job%20fair%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20done%20two%20internships%20during%20her%20undergraduate%20at%20Teresian%20College%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20admits%20to%20her%20classmates%20taking%20pictures%20of%20her%20and%20mocking%20her%20for%20her%20height%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20affect%20her%20marks%20and%20her%20morale.%20But%20she%20took%20a%20stand%20for%20herself%20which%20helped%20her%20blossom%20personally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20message%20to%20her%20bullies%3F%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20treat%20anyone%20else%20the%20way%20you%20treated%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Disha%20shares%20how%20she%20got%20her%20first%20job%20offer%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20small%20ICICI%20home-loan%20third-party%20office%20after%20giving%2017%20interviews.%20When%20she%20finished%20her%20graduation%20in%20early%202000s%2C%20there%20were%20no%20online%20job%20portals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20only%20classified%20columns%20in%20newspapers%2C%20and%20walk-in%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20an%20experience%20of%20going%20to%20Sab%20TV%20for%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20response%20she%20was%20met%20was%20this%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESab%20kuch%20theek%20hai%2C%20par%20aap%20thode%20alag%20ho%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Everything%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20you%20are%20a%20bit%20different).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20told%20that%20the%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20may%20not%20be%20comfortable%20with%20her%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20is%20not%20something%20that%20most%20corporate%20organisations%20in%20India%20are%20too%20keen%20on%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20it%20as%20directly%20generating%20income%20or%20business%20for%20their%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20social%20awareness%20on%20disability%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20organisations%20have%20understood%20the%20need%20to%20back%20diverse%20candidates%20and%20have%20started%20to%20more%20thoroughly%20follow%20the%20ES%26amp%3BT%20(Employments%20through%20Skills%2C%20Training%20and%20Placement)%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConducting%20a%20job%20fair%20which%20spreads%20awareness%20on%20issues%20like%20disabilities%2C%20socio-economic%20marginalisation%20and%20caste%2C%20something%20that%20most%20organisations%20shy%20away%20from%2C%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Ratnaprabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20people%20not%20to%20judge%20individuals%20based%20on%20their%20disabilities%2C%20Disha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20judgemental%20is%20a%20disability%20itself%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20visible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Disha%20Pandya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10009251%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCensus%25202011%2520and%2520recently%2520held%2C2011%252C%2520respectively%2520(4)%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10009251%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCensus%25202011%2520and%2520recently%2520held%2C2011%252C%2520respectively%2520(4)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2FBillsTexts%2FLSBillTexts%2FAsintroduced%2F40%2520of%25202022%2520(As%2520introduced).pdf%3Fsource%3Dlegislation%23%3A~%3Atext%3D(1)%2520This%2520Act%2520may%2520be%2C5%2520Short%2520title%2520and%2520commencement%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2FBillsTexts%2FLSBillTexts%2FAsintroduced%2F40%2520of%25202022%2520(As%2520introduced).pdf%3Fsource%3Dlegislation%23%3A~%3Atext%3D(1)%2520This%2520Act%2520may%2520be%2C5%2520Short%2520title%2520and%2520commencement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20With%20Disabilities%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202022%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lpaonline.org%2Ffaq-%23%3A~%3Atext%3DQ%253A%2520What%2520is%2520the%2520definition%2Cbe%2520slightly%2520taller%2520than%2520that%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.lpaonline.org%2Ffaq-%23%3A~%3Atext%3DQ%253A%2520What%2520is%2520the%2520definition%2Cbe%2520slightly%2520taller%2520than%2520that%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Little%20People%20of%20America%20%E2%80%93%20Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721660750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-1721660148.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20their%20abilities%2C%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20often%20face%20biases%20due%20to%20their%20stature.%20For%20the%20last%206%20years%2C%20Disha%20Pandya%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20community%20gets%20the%20right%20exposure.%20Through%20her%20initiative%2C%20Little%20People%20Of%20India%2C%20she%20is%20helping%20others%20find%20corporate%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tanvi%20Dalvi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357760%2Fdisability-dwarfism-jobs-employment-diversity-vividhataa-disha-pandya-little-people-of-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Couple%20Quit%20Jobs%20To%20Turn%20Family%20Land%20into%20Self-Sustaining%20Farm%2C%20Teach%2015000%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20your%20purpose%20in%20life%3F%E2%80%99%20Couple%20Gnana%20Saravanan%20and%20Krishnasudha%20were%20pondering%20over%20this%20quintessential%20question%20as%20they%20sipped%20their%20morning%20tea.%20Both%20IT%20professionals%20worked%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20of%20Chennai%20in%20private%20companies%2C%20far%20from%20their%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354716%2Fvegetable-farmer-smarika-chandrakar-grows-tomatoes-cucumbers-brinjals-in-chhattisgarh-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeighth-generation%20farmer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20first%20in%20his%20family%20to%20graduate%20from%20college.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20missed%20the%20lush%20greenery%20of%20his%20family%20farm%20in%20Palakkad%2C%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20purpose%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20work%20for%20corporations.%20As%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20responsibility%20to%20give%20back%20to%20my%20roots%20and%20help%20sustain%20our%20generational%20farm.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20the%20income%20from%20farming%20that%20provided%20for%20my%20education%20and%20that%20of%20my%20siblings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saravanan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnasudha%20too%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20always%20wished%20to%20retain%20the%20lush%20greenery%20that%20a%20farm%20life%20offered.%20This%20was%20a%20pact%20that%20they%20drew%20when%20they%20first%20met%20each%20other%20for%20marriage%2C%20she%20laughs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20both%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20the%20farm%20after%20working%20for%20a%20few%20years%20in%20corporate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20couple%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20returned%20to%20Palakkad%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20they%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20and%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20transformed%20their%20farm%20since%20is%20an%20inspiring%20lesson%20for%20many.%20By%20leveraging%20technology%20for%20good%2C%20they%20mechanised%20the%20entire%20farming%20process%2C%20from%20creating%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20setting%20up%20efficient%20irrigation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20developed%20value-added%20products%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20ghee%2C%20all%20produced%20at%20their%20farm%2C%20Deesan%20Farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20model%20organic%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%2036%20acres%20of%20land%20where%20they%20primarily%20grew%20coconuts.%20Although%20they%20practised%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-irrigation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20input%20costs%20were%20very%20high.%20Upon%20returning%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20the%2039-year-old%20did%20was%20to%20implement%20integrated%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20has%20made%20his%20farm%20self-sufficient%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20has%20made%20his%20farm%20self-sufficient%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20integrated%20farming%20system%20is%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20crop-livestock%20farming%20that%20combines%20agricultural%20production%2C%20animal%20management%2C%20and%20resource%20management.%20Its%20goal%20is%20to%20reduce%20external%20inputs%20and%20achieve%20self-sufficiency%20by%20using%20technology%20to%20recycle%20all%20wastes%20into%20fertilisers.%20Key%20components%20of%20this%20system%20include%20intercropping%2C%20advanced%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20efficient%20recycling%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20three%20major%20issues%20in%20farming%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoil%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWaste%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20an%20integrated%20farm%2C%20Saravanan%20first%20added%20a%20dairy%20farm%20with%2020%20cows.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20the%20output%20(dung)%20given%20by%20the%20cows%20that%20he%20designed%20the%20entire%20farm.%20The%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20are%20converted%20into%20natural%20fertilisers%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Epanchagavya%2C%20jeevamruth%2C%20amirtha%20karaisal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vermicompost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20answers%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20are%20present%20in%20traditional%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20my%20forefathers%20and%20father%20in%20building%20this%20farm%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20waste.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20practising%20soil%20conservation%20and%20balancing%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20ages.%20I%20use%20their%20knowledge%20with%20a%20small%20twist%20of%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20the%20fertilisers%20manually%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20biodigester%2C%20which%20produces%20seven%20times%20the%20output%20that%20was%20being%20produced%20earlier.%20All%20the%20waste%20generated%20in%20the%20cow%20shed%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20fermentation%20chamber%2C%20generating%20almost%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20fertilisers%20daily%2C%20as%20per%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Deesan%20Organic%20Farms%20(%40deesan_organic_farms)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20fertilisers%20are%20mixed%20and%20applied%20to%20the%20plantations%20every%2015%20days.%20The%20vermicompost%20unit%20generates%20almost%201.5%20tonnes%20of%20vermicompost%20every%20month.%20A%20biogas%20unit%20utilises%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cow%20dung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20these%20machines%2C%20Saravanan%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20microclimate%20while%20generating%20more%20income%20through%20intercropping.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20farm%20had%20monocropping%20with%201%2C650%20coconut%20trees.%20Saravanan%20added%20banana%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20areca%20nut%20amidst%20the%20coconut%20trees.%20Besides%20this%2C%20he%20added%20guava%20and%20papaya%20on%20open%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20created%20biodiversity%2C%20giving%20us%20financial%20and%20biological%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20creating%20a%20self-sustained%20farm%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20to%20create%20a%20market%20for%20the%20products.%20For%20this%2C%20Krishnasudha%20stepped%20in%20and%20suggested%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356941%2Forganic-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores-earthy-tales-delhi-ncr-deepak-sabharwal-rajasthan-farm-pesticides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20set%20up%20a%20production%20unit%20on%20their%20farm%20itself%20with%20a%20solar%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20experience%20here.%20There%20is%20lesser%20stress%20as%20compared%20to%20a%20corporate%20job%20with%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20serving%20good%20products%20to%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Deesan%20Farms%20makes%20a%20tonne%20of%20coconut%20oil%20and%20250%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Eper%20week%2C%20claims%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20youngsters%20interested%20in%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Saravanan%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20about%20farming%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandparents%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20natural%20farming%20course.%20He%20says%20that%20this%20helped%20him%20with%20better%20ways%20of%20creating%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudents%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%2C%20named%20after%20his%20father%2C%20Jagadeeshan%20is%20today%20a%20model%20farm%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20organic%20farming.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Kera%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Yuva%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Akshayasree%20Award%202022-23%20for%20Best%20Organic%20Farming%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20farm%20was%20set%20up%20and%20started%20running%20smoothly%2C%20he%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge%20with%20the%20next%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CMerely%20one%20person%20practising%20a%20sustainable%20model%20of%20farming%20is%20of%20no%20good%20if%20that%20information%20is%20not%20shared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20educate%20other%20farmers%20and%20students%20about%20healthy%20ways%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20consume%20food%20and%20practice%20farming%20that%20is%20beneficial%20to%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20conducts%20classes%20for%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20under%20the%20Bhartiya%20Prakritik%20Krishi%20Paddhti%20(BPKP)%20and%20the%20Paramparagath%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PKVY)%20scheme.%20With%20at%20least%20three%20classes%20per%20week%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20educated%20over%2015%2C000%20farmers%20and%20students%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreedhu%20P%2C%20agricultural%20officer%2C%20Perumatty%2C%20says%20that%20Saravanan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20how%20an%20organic%20farm%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201090px)%20100vw%2C%201090px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%201090w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-204x300.jpeg%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-500x734.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-768x1127.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-1046x1536.jpeg%201046w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med